Package: cleaningkit
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 2026.07.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Abubakar", "Athman", , "abubakar.athman@mixedmigration.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package offers an automated toolkit for streamlining 4Mi
    survey data cleaning and validation, enforcing protocols on data
    quality, sampling, and enumerator performance. It provides a
    standardized approach to checking interview consistency, identifying
    outliers, "other" text responses, and detecting potential fraud based
    on official SOPs.
